org.fileprocessor

Class DefaultFileProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fileprocessor.DefaultFileProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileProcessor

    public class DefaultFileProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileProcessor
    Default implementation for files that do not require interactive access to intermediate results of the processing. It implements a well defined interface for basic file processing @Link FileProcessor.
